#giveaway #slime #slimeshop #slimers #slimegiveaway

🍌PEELERZ BANANA
What's your favorite fruit?

This texture is just like the soft, chewy center of a Peelerz gummy! 🍌 The fluffy ky-scream base puffs up beautifully when you mix in the adorable handmade clay banana slices—and yes, it even comes with a tiny palm tree to complete the tropical vibe! Soothing, squishy, and super beginner-friendly, this slime is perfect for anyone who loves a calming sensory experience. Scented exactly like Peelerz Banana—sweet, creamy, and absolutely irresistible!🍌

🥭We brought back Mango Peelerz from our Viral Candy release a while back! Just to commemorate the occasion! 

🙏THANK YOU @peelerzhawaii & @enjoysnacks808 for  the most yummiest inspiration!

❤️PEELERZ LYCHEE
Gummies or chocolate? 

Get hands-on and craft your own lychee fruits with this jam-packed bingsu DIY! The vibrant red bingsu color is stunning!  Mix it with the thick icee base slime, it transforms into a silky soufflé-jelly bingsu texture—soft, squishy, bubbly, and full of satisfying crackles. Scented just like Peelerz' iconic lychee gummy, using our signature lychee blend. It's spot-on and absolutely mouthwatering! 💕🫶

🔥GET 15% & 10% OFF ALL 3 NEW PEELERS SLIMES!

🍍PEELERZ PINEAPPLE 🍍 
What Peelerz flavors have you tried? 

One of Hawaii’s favorite Peelerz flavors brought to life in slime form! 🍍 This tropical DIY features a clear bingsu floam base that’s extra crunchy and satisfying on its own. When you mix in the pineapple skin clay piece, it gets puffed up into a crackly, airy whipped texture!  Feel free to just play with the base, and then you can add in the clay when you are ready.  Scented just like dreamy pineapple candy!
